snippet.title: GoUpGoat - In Game Video
snippet.description: Video from the game play of Go Up Goat. All the levels you can see are autogenerated. The higher level become more and more complex and difficult. The video is taken from the Mac OS X version. Available here: https://itunes.apple.com/de/app/go-up-goat-gug/id1236435035?l=en&mt=12
